{
  "chapter": 34,
  "chapter_summary": "第34章\"活死人\"讲述了芮玮与林琼菊前往湘妃神庵寻找野儿的故事。一灯神尼因芮玮未学全海渊八剑而拒绝让他见野儿，并要求他自断一足。林琼菊出言不逊激怒一灯，芮玮为保护她与一灯展开激战。芮玮虽只学六剑，但凭借飞龙八步和化神掌与一灯周旋，最终被一灯用拂尘暗算重伤。神秘老人活死人及时出现救下芮玮，迫使一灯认输并让芮玮去见野儿。然而野儿已留书出走，芮玮闻讯昏厥。本章展现了芮玮的武功成长、一灯的严厉性格以及活死人的神秘身份，为后续野儿出走埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "她们个个身怀一种绝艺，有的会弹琴、吹箫；有的会诗书绘画；更有的精擅刺绣，至于武功皆都不弱，她们每个将绝艺传我，我一时哪学得那么多！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "她们的绝艺可全是蓝髯客传的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我真想不到那个蓝胡子大汉那么多本领，难怪他的弟子皆甘心在这雪岭上跟他学艺，他的本领实在了不得。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你既然羡慕蓝髯客的本领，也跟他在这雪岭上学艺吧。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥若要我与你分离，天下再有趣的事也吸引不了我。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "晚辈芮玮求见神尼！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "八剑学全没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "神尼嘱咐，晚辈未能达成，八剑只学六剑，因……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "未学全来做什么？限你盏茶以内离去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮玮，你怎么还没离去？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "老前辈可就是一灯神尼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "谁是老前辈，前辈就是前辈，还要加个老字，莫非有意来气我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "前辈，晚辈见野儿一面，不知她近来好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你管她好不好，我说过的话你敢不听？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "前辈嘱七情魔相传的话，晚辈记得，只是晚辈见野儿一面就好，不敢多求。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "念你取得天龙珠治好野儿的腿伤，才给你盏茶时间离去，你不知好歹还敢留在这里，不能再饶，快快自行绝去一足，莫要我来动手。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "喂！你这位老尼怎么不讲理啊？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好啊！你敢用海渊剑法来挡我佛珠，不让我杀那丫头，敢情要自己杀她，也好，快快动手。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "前辈无缘无故，为何要杀她？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你可是在教训我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "不敢！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "谅你不敢。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮玮，你是活得不耐烦了吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "纵然她有对前辈不敬之处，罪不致死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你要见野儿，与野儿和好，就得替我杀了她。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "要杀她才能见野儿，野儿知道也不会答应。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不杀，我来杀，倘若你再敢阻止，顾不得野儿怪我，也要杀你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "出家人何必尽言'杀'字？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "数十年没有人敢再逆我心意，今日竟有人一再逆我心意，说不得我要大开杀戒了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "今日你只要胜我手中拂尘，不但饶这丫头一命，野儿任你去见。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "还有一招守势，芮玮，你看能否守住。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好啊，你还藏着看家本领。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "小子，你欺我太甚！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "今日杀你，怪我不得。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吾命休矣！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "speaker_name": "活死人",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "阿玉，你怎么又杀人！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "speaker_name": "活死人",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "快止气闭穴。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "speaker_name": "活死人",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "小姑娘别担心，他没事了，只要好好休养不要动伤口，一月即愈。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "text": "活死人，又是你来管我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "speaker_name": "活死人",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "阿玉，你答应不再杀人，只要你不杀人我便不管你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "text": "我不杀他们，活死人，你该走了吧？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "speaker_name": "活死人",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "这件事我既管了，就要管到底，我不能走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "text": "你还要管什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "speaker_name": "活死人",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "阿玉，你别生气，我就在松树上观看，你用拂尘击伤芮玮那时，我还准备不管，但你见他伤了还要杀，就不得不管了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "text": "我才不会在你面前生气，你到底要管什么，快说出来，这次我还是听你的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "speaker_name": "活死人",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "第一，该承认输给了芮玮。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "text": "我用拂尘他仅空手，尚战个二百招不败，果然该算他得胜，我认输了又有何妨。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "speaker_name": "活死人",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "第二……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "text": "没有第二，咱们说好的，每次你只得管一件事，说话不能不算数。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_si_ren",
      "speaker_name": "活死人",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "我没有要管第二件事啊？只是这第二要你记得说话不能不算数，你既承认输了，就该让芮玮去见你的高徒。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "算你厉害，我每次在你手中，就连说话也说不过你，芮玮，别再装死，快起来跟我去见野儿。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_ye_er",
      "text": "野儿，野儿！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "你……你……竟将她关在这里……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我的徒儿怎么不能关，她不听我吩咐，竟和喻百龙的徒弟相处一起，难道不该关吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "text": "我是我师父的弟子，又不是坏人，为何野儿不能与我相处一起。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我说不能在一起，就不能在一起。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_deng_shen_ni",
      "speaker_name": "一灯神尼",
      "listener": "char_ye_er",
      "text": "好丫头，敢背我偷偷逃走。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
